name: Flowers Makin Whoopee
description: The perfect marriage between AI & classical music, in “Flowers Makin Whoopee” borders between flowers get blurred. Generated by a GAN trained on 14,000 flowers, the flowers dance to “Makin Whoopee," a classic jazz/blues song turned on its head. The sultry violin and booming plucks of the cello immerse you in a world reminiscent of a time gone by. Holders receive a private streamed cello concert & an AI art lesson; email nathan@nathanchancello.com to verify. Lia Coleman, Nathan Chan, Andy Liang.
